      <content eId="content_1">
        <p>The Camara de Ingredientes hereby transmits the <ref href="/akn/poc/bill/paella-reform-2024">Bill to Reform the Valencian Paella Recipe</ref>, approved in plenary session on June 15, 2024.</p>
        <p>The bill was approved with the following amendments incorporated: <ref href="/akn/poc/amendment/amendment-optional-socarrat">Optional Socarrat</ref>. The <ref href="/akn/poc/amendment/amendment-brown-rice">Brown Rice Amendment</ref> was rejected.</p>
      </content>

      <rationale eId="rat_1">
        <heading>Rationale</heading>
        <p>The bill was approved by a vote of 28 in favor, 12 against, and 5 abstentions. It is transmitted for Senado review per Article 72 of the Parliamentary Rules.</p>
      </rationale>
